algTester
=========

About:
	This is a program that displays the results of openCV's image processing in openGL.
	It can be used to generate test cases (still being worked on) and compare the final
	results.

How to use:
	algTester [image] [rotation rate (degrees) ]

Controls:
	<w,s> .....................	Zoom In/Out of Image
	<a> + <left mouse> ........ Add user identified result
	<d> .......................	Mark selected result as false positive or 
								delete selected user identified result
	<e> .......................	Mark selected result as positive
	<left mouse> ..............	Track/Pan
	<right mouse> .............	Select result

Dependencies:
	glut, opencv

Correct order to see results:
	make
	make demo1